					<p class="lead">Team Buckeye needs a tool with which they can intelligently and efficiently connect Pelotonia participants with Pelotonia-related practice events. The application will make it easier for people to particpate in Pelotonia, a cycling event that raises money for cancer research. Pelotonia is the largest cycling event in the United States.</p>

        </div>
      </div>
