  <footer id="apply"> <!-- footer begings -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
					<h2 class="section-title">Apply to Participate</h2>
					<div class="row spacer40"></div>
					<h3 class="text-center">Why is it necessary to apply?</h3>
					<p>This is the first time that we are running an event of this kind. Thus, we want to keep the group size small so as not to become too overwhelming of a crowd to manage.</p>
					<div class="row spacer40"></div>
					<h3 class="text-center">What skills are needed?</h3>
					<p>In general, the event will be heavily oriented toward individuals with technical or design skills. However, if you are interested in being a product manager please apply. If you don't have design, UX, programming or management skills but are still interested in participating, tell us why you would like to be involved and what you feel you can bring to the team.</p>
					<div class="row spacer40"></div>
					<h3 class="text-center">Is it first come, first serve?</h3>
					<p>No. Preference will be given to more senior students who are closer to graduating. If you are a freshman or sophomore and would still like to participate, please tell us why you should be a part of the team. A good collection of past work and clear passion and interest to learn will go a long way towards acceptance.</p>
					<div class="row spacer40"></div>
					<h3 class="text-center">Should I still apply?</h3>
					<p>Absolutely!! This is only the beginning.</p>
					<p>We are planning on hosting additional events in the Fall of 2015 and Spring 2016. In addition, we will have free training sessions prior to future events. If you apply now and are not accepted, you will be put on the waiting list and automatically entered to participate in the next event and benefit from exclusive training on the latest technologies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row spacer40"></div>    
      <div class="row">
				<%= form_for(@event_application, remote: true) do |f| %>
          <div class="col-xs-12">
            
            <div class="row">            
              <div class="form-group col-xs-6">
								<%= f.label :name, "Full Name" %>
								<%= f.text_field :name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Name" %>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-xs-6">
                <%# <label for="email2">email</label> %>
								<%= f.label :email %>
								<%= f.text_field :email, class: "form-control", placeholder: "E-mail" %> 
              </div>
            </div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="form-group col-xs-6">
								<%= f.label :github_account_name, "Github User Name" %>
								<%= f.text_field :github_account_name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "mygithub" %>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group col-xs-6">
								<%= f.label :language_preference, "Programming Language Preference" %>
								<%= f.text_field :language_preference, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Python, Lisp, C, Haskell" %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="form-group col-xs-6">
								<%= f.label :university_year, "Year at University" %>
								<%= f.select :university_year, options_for_select(["Freshman", "Sophomore", "Junior", "Senior", "5th Year", "Other", "Not Applicable"]), {}, class: "form-control" %>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group col-xs-6">
								<%= f.label :work_preference, "What do you prefer working on?" %>
								<%= f.select :work_preference, options_for_select(["Design/UX", "Front-End", "Back-End", "API", "Database", "DevOps/Deployment"]), {}, class: "form-control" %>
							</div>
						</div>
            
            <div class="row">            
              <div class="form-group col-xs-12">
                <%# <label for="message2">message</label> %>
								<%= f.label :message, "Questions or Comments" %>
								<%= f.text_area :message, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Message", rows: 8 %>

              </div>
            </div> 
            <div class="row spacer30"></div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                <p class="text-center">Please, fill out the form and press submit.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row spacer10"></div>
            <div class="row">            
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
							<div class="alert alert-success" id="contact_form_success" style="display:none;">The e-mail was successfully sent. Thank you. We will reach back out to you as soon as we possibly can.</div>
							<div class="error alert alert-danger" id="err-form">There is a problem with the contact form, please verify that all the fields are filled out correctly.</div>
            <div class="error" id="err-timedout">The connection to the server timed out!</div>
            <div class="error" id="err-state"></div>
              
                <%# <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default" id="send">Submit</button> %>
								<%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-default" %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>  
					
				<% end %>
      </div>      
